Suresh   Vasudevan  Chief Executive Officer and Director, Nimble Storage, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 3 Board Members in 3 different organizations across 6 different industries.See Board Relationships46$7,152,031As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Suresh Vasudevan has been the Chief Executive Officer at Nimble Storage, Inc. since March 2011 and served as its President. Mr. Vasudevan served as a Senior Vice President and General Manager of Networked Storage & Manageability Group at NetApp, Inc. He was responsible for overseeing the Decru product strategy, as well as participating in strategic business planning and development for Decru product offerings. He served as the President at Nimble Storage, Inc. He ... served as Senior Vice President of Network Appliance at Decru, Inc. He served as the Chief Executive Officer and President of Omneon, Inc. at Harmonic Inc. from January 2009 to February 1, 2011. He joined NetApp in 1999 as a Senior Manager of Business Development and later become Director of Strategic Alliances. In these roles, he helped establish and manage alliances with OEMs and led partner initiatives with global systems integrators and channel partners. As a Senior Director of Software, he managed product marketing, planning and strategic partnerships for the Systems and Application Software division of NetApp. He served at the management consulting firm McKinsey & Co. in New Delhi, Mumbai and Chicago as a Senior Engagement Manager, focusing on product marketing, operations and marketing strategy. He served as the Chairman of Nimble Storage, Inc. from September 2013 to April 17, 2017. He has been a Member of Advisory Board at Glassbeam, Inc. since December 12, 2016. He has been Director at Datos IO, Inc. since June 21, 2017. He has been a Director at Nimble Storage, Inc. since September 2009. He served as a Director of Cirtas Systems, Inc. since January 25, 2011 He served as a Director of Glassbeam, Inc. until December 12, 2016. He served as a Director of Amoeba Capital Partners. He served as a Director of Omneon, Inc. Mr. Vasudevan holds a B.S. degree in Electrical Engineering, with honors, from the Birla Institute of Technology and Science (BITS) in Pilani, India and an M.B.A. from the Indian Institute of Management (IIM) in Calcutta, India. He holds a Post Graduate Diploma in Management from Indian Institute of Management (IIM) in Calcutta, India.Read Full Background




